 democracy.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aCitizenshipxStudy and teachingxUnited States. 0aCitizenshipxStudy and teachingzUnited States. 0aCivicsxStudy and teachingxUnited States. 0aCivicsxStudy and teachingzUnited States. 0aEducationxAims and objectivesxUnited States. 0aEducationxAims and objectiveszUnited States. 0aÉducation civiquexÉtats-Unis. 0aÉducationxFinalitésxÉtats-UnisxUnited States. 7aEDUCATION / Philosophy, Theory & Social Aspects.2bisacsh1 aDamon, William, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aElshtain, Jean Bethke, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGlazer, Nathan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGlenn, Charles L., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGrant, Gerald, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHillygus, D. Sunshine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHolmes, Mark, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNie, Norman, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNord, Warren A., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPutnam, Robert D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRakove, Jack N., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRavitch, Diane, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRavitch, Diane, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aSalomone, Rosemary C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aViteritti, Joseph P., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aViteritti, Joseph P., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relator